.DT
host
Discworld creator help
host

.SH Name
.SI 5
host - Lookup a hostname or IP address.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
dest <ip-address, host or player>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Just like the nslookup and host commands for UNIX, this command will
lookup an IP address (and resolve it to a hostname) or vice-versa.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
host arienne
host discworld.imaginary.com
host 127.0.0.1
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
netstat
.EP
